[grunts]

1338
01:52:01.416 --> 01:52:02.666
[electricity crackling]

1339
01:52:02.750 --> 01:52:03.833
[metal creaking]

1340
01:52:06.125 --> 01:52:07.250
[electricity crackles]

1341
01:52:08.416 --> 01:52:09.666
[babbles]

1342
01:52:10.875 --> 01:52:12.708
[♪ Gentle music plays]

1343
01:52:24.541 --> 01:52:26.375
[speaks Huttese]

1344
01:52:26.458 --> 01:52:28.166
[Hutt Sister speaks Huttese]

1345
01:52:28.250 --> 01:52:30.333
[in Huttese] Wait! We know much.

1346
01:52:30.416 --> 01:52:31.916
Go help Rotta.

1347
01:52:33.583 --> 01:52:35.125
[Hutt Brother speaks Huttese]

1348
01:52:35.208 --> 01:52:37.750
- [Hutt Brother speaks Huttese]
- [Hutt Sister speaks Huttese]

1349
01:52:39.041 --> 01:52:40.041
[speaks Huttese]

1350
01:52:40.125 --> 01:52:41.666
You saw my face.

1351
01:52:42.583 --> 01:52:43.333
[in Huttese] Stop!

1352
01:52:43.416 --> 01:52:44.250
[Hutt Sister gasping]

1353
01:52:44.333 --> 01:52:45.833
Now it's time to die.

1354
01:52:55.708 --> 01:52:56.750
[grunts]

1355
01:53:01.791 --> 01:53:03.000
[grunts]

1356
01:53:05.333 --> 01:53:07.750
[♪ Majestic music plays]

1357
01:53:09.166 --> 01:53:10.208
[machinery powers down]

1358
01:53:10.875 --> 01:53:12.208
[sighs]

1359
01:53:13.916 --> 01:53:15.416
[♪ Tense music plays]

1360
01:53:22.000 --> 01:53:23.000
[Embo grunts]

1361
01:53:25.041 --> 01:53:26.541
[both grunting]

1362
01:53:27.208 --> 01:53:28.208
[Embo grunts]

1363
01:53:30.791 --> 01:53:32.250
[The Mandalorian shouts]

1364
01:53:33.875 --> 01:53:35.625
[Embo grunting]

1365
01:53:37.666 --> 01:53:38.666
[both grunt]

1366
01:53:40.041 --> 01:53:41.791
[Grogu exclaims. groans]

1367
01:53:43.250 --> 01:53:44.500
[Hutt Brother growls]

1368
01:53:47.208 --> 01:53:48.500
[grunts]

1369
01:53:49.208 --> 01:53:51.375
- [whimpers]
- [slurps]

1370
01:53:51.458 --> 01:53:52.833
[growls]

1371
01:53:53.750 --> 01:53:54.791
[growls]

1372
01:53:54.875 --> 01:53:56.035
[in English] Leave him alone!

1373
01:53:57.666 --> 01:53:58.666
[groans]

1374
01:53:59.416 --> 01:54:01.333
[both grunting. roaring]

1375
01:54:07.000 --> 01:54:08.000
[grunts]

1376
01:54:10.000 --> 01:54:11.000
[grunts]

1377
01:54:12.125 --> 01:54:13.541
[weapon clatters]

1378
01:54:15.625 --> 01:54:17.416
[grunts. pants]

1379
01:54:18.125 --> 01:54:20.916
[in Huttese] You don't have Jabba to protect you.

1380
01:54:21.500 --> 01:54:22.958
I'm not little anymore!

1381
01:54:25.291 --> 01:54:26.916
[all grunting]

1382
01:54:34.583 --> 01:54:35.583
[snarls]

1383
01:54:36.333 --> 01:54:37.333
[growls]

1384
01:54:38.541 --> 01:54:39.541
[Embo grunts]

1385
01:54:43.291 --> 01:54:44.375
[The Mandalorian grunts]

1386
01:54:47.041 --> 01:54:49.750
[growling]

1387
01:54:50.458 --> 01:54:51.458
[snarls]

1388
01:54:56.250 --> 01:54:57.333
[Force rumbling]

1389
01:55:08.750 --> 01:55:10.625
[both grunting]

1390
01:55:14.000 --> 01:55:15.666
[Rotta shouts]

1391
01:55:25.208 --> 01:55:27.208
[♪ Gentle music plays]

1392
01:55:27.291 --> 01:55:28.666
[Keibu snoring]

1393
01:55:30.583 --> 01:55:32.458
[both grunting]

1394
01:55:33.583 --> 01:55:34.583
[grunts]

1395
01:55:38.625 --> 01:55:39.625
[Embo grunts]

1396
01:55:41.166 --> 01:55:42.333
[snarls]

1397
01:55:45.500 --> 01:55:47.458
[Hutt Brother. Rotta grunting]

1398
01:55:54.208 --> 01:55:57.458
[in Huttese] Stop! You'll kill us all!

1399
01:55:58.666 --> 01:56:00.291
[Hutts yell]

1400
01:56:06.333 --> 01:56:08.833
[Force rumbling]

1401
01:56:08.916 --> 01:56:12.333
[♪ Uplifting music plays]

1402
01:56:27.458 --> 01:56:28.541
[gasps]

1403
01:56:35.083 --> 01:56:37.916
[both groaning]

1404
01:56:40.250 --> 01:56:41.625
[roars]

1405
01:56:42.000 --> 01:56:43.541
[in Huttese] Save us. bounty hunter!

1406
01:56:44.916 --> 01:56:45.916
Keibu. [Speaks Kyuzo]

1407
01:56:46.000 --> 01:56:47.666
[in Huttese] Save us!

1408
01:56:48.208 --> 01:56:50.166
[Hutt Brother speaks Huttese]

1409
01:56:50.875 --> 01:56:52.833
[Hutt Brother exclaims]

1410
01:56:53.375 --> 01:56:55.125
- [screams]
- [Hutt brother groaning]

1411
01:57:00.083 --> 01:57:01.375
[groans]

1412
01:57:02.708 --> 01:57:03.708
[screams]

1413
01:57:14.916 --> 01:57:16.333
[metal banging]

1414
01:57:16.416 --> 01:57:18.166
[♪ Tense music plays]

1415
01:57:19.708 --> 01:57:21.458
[banging continues]

1416
01:57:22.000 --> 01:57:24.666
We don't have much time. We have to get out of here.

1417
01:57:25.625 --> 01:57:26.833
Is there another way out?

1418
01:57:26.916 --> 01:57:29.583
- I think it's that way.
- Go. Go!

1419
01:57:46.083 --> 01:57:47.083
Target sighted.

1420
01:57:47.875 --> 01:57:48.875
[droid yells]

1421
01:58:11.250 --> 01:58:12.916
[static on comms]

1422
01:58:13.000 --> 01:58:13.916
Hello?

1423
01:58:14.000 --> 01:58:15.880
[Anzellan 1 through comms] <i>Mando! We came back.</i>

1424
01:58:15.958 --> 01:58:17.208
- What?
- We came back.

1425
01:58:17.291 --> 01:58:19.000
We told you we would.

1426
01:58:19.083 --> 01:58:21.083
[♪ Hopeful music plays]

1427
01:58:26.041 --> 01:58:29.000
[Ward] <i>Adelphi Squadron. entering atmosphere.</i>

1428
01:58:29.958 --> 01:58:32.666
- What's your status. Mando?
- <i>We're under attack.</i>

1429
01:58:33.666 --> 01:58:35.000
There are too many.

1430
01:58:35.083 --> 01:58:37.083
Fire everything you have at my location.

1431
01:58:38.625 --> 01:58:41.833
- [Ward] <i>Your location?</i>
- Yes. my location.

1432
01:58:41.916 --> 01:58:43.416
I can't give that order.

1433
01:58:43.500 --> 01:58:44.916
Don't worry...

1434
01:58:46.916 --> 01:58:49.125
we'll be out of here by the time you do.

1435
01:58:50.750 --> 01:58:51.791
Good luck.

1436
01:58:51.875 --> 01:58:53.250
[X-wing engines screeching]

1437
01:58:55.375 --> 01:58:56.666
Blue Leader to squadron.

1438
01:58:57.250 --> 01:59:00.291
<i>assume defensive formation. prepare to engage.</i>

1439
01:59:00.375 --> 01:59:01.541
All weapons hot.

1440
01:59:01.625 --> 01:59:02.625
Copy that.

1441
01:59:14.250 --> 01:59:15.875
[droid chatter]

1442
01:59:20.083 --> 01:59:21.833
Enemy fighters approaching.

1443
01:59:21.916 --> 01:59:23.916
[♪ Heroic music plays]

1444
01:59:24.000 --> 01:59:25.000
Here they come.

1445
01:59:32.750 --> 01:59:34.000
[Rotta grunting]

1446
01:59:34.666 --> 01:59:35.750
[Rotta roars]

1447
01:59:35.833 --> 01:59:37.041
[droid beeps]

1448
01:59:46.541 --> 01:59:47.666
[chuckles]

1449
01:59:52.166 --> 01:59:53.500
Turbolasers. up ahead.

1450
01:59:53.583 --> 01:59:54.750
Got it.

1451
02:00:15.625 --> 02:00:17.041
I've got one on my tail.

1452
02:00:19.750 --> 02:00:21.250
I got you.

1453
02:00:27.250 --> 02:00:28.250
[squeaks]

1454
02:00:31.416 --> 02:00:33.041
- [cheers]
- Yippee! Yay!

1455
02:00:33.125 --> 02:00:34.708
Taking out the launch tubes.

1456
02:00:42.458 --> 02:00:45.333
Blue Leader to Red Jammer. mark it and lock it in.

1457
02:00:47.833 --> 02:00:48.958
Locking in target.

1458
02:00:52.666 --> 02:00:53.708
It's a dead end.

1459
02:00:55.000 --> 02:00:56.416
We're trapped.

1460
02:00:57.125 --> 02:00:58.333
Stand back.

1461
02:01:04.708 --> 02:01:06.101
[Ward through comms] <i>We're closing fast.</i>

1462
02:01:06.125 --> 02:01:07.541
Repeat. we're closing fast.

1463
02:01:07.625 --> 02:01:09.208
You better be out of there. Mando.

1464
02:01:09.291 --> 02:01:10.708
[The Mandalorian] Jump.

1465
02:01:10.791 --> 02:01:12.875
[Rotta] That's a long way down.

1466
02:01:12.958 --> 02:01:14.166
Closing on target.

1467
02:01:15.708 --> 02:01:18.059
- [The Mandalorian] Gotta jump.
- [Rotta] Moat's not that deep.

1468
02:01:18.083 --> 02:01:20.125
It's a bomber. Jump.

1469
02:01:20.208 --> 02:01:22.000
Let's light up this swamp.

1470
02:01:33.083 --> 02:01:34.375
[yelling]

1471
02:01:56.791 --> 02:01:58.416
[pilot] <i>Anybody got eyes on Mando?</i>

1472
02:01:59.083 --> 02:02:00.083
There they are.

1473
02:02:00.666 --> 02:02:02.958
[♪ Uplifting music plays]

1474
02:02:04.500 --> 02:02:08.250
Zeb. go collect the trash.

1475
02:02:16.375 --> 02:02:19.166
I'm getting a little tired of these hot extractions.

1476
02:02:20.083 --> 02:02:22.041
- What took you so long?
- [Grogu babbles]

1477
02:02:22.125 --> 02:02:23.291
[chuckles]

1478
02:02:23.375 --> 02:02:24.500
Hop in.

1479
02:02:24.583 --> 02:02:26.416
Let's head home.

1480
02:02:31.750 --> 02:02:33.750
[♪ Triumphant music plays]

1481
02:02:49.333 --> 02:02:50.708
Colonel.

1482
02:02:53.041 --> 02:02:54.416
Messy.

1483
02:02:55.000 --> 02:02:56.250
Very messy.

1484
02:02:57.458 --> 02:02:59.083
Why'd you come for me?

1485
02:02:59.166 --> 02:03:00.666
That wasn't part of the mission.

1486
02:03:01.416 --> 02:03:04.541
You were right. Coin told us everything.

1487
02:03:05.041 --> 02:03:06.666
The Twins were playing us.

1488
02:03:06.750 --> 02:03:09.291
Feeding information to the Empire all along.

1489
02:03:10.625 --> 02:03:13.291
They picked a side. It wasn't ours.

1490
02:03:13.916 --> 02:03:17.541
Besides. we don't leave our own behind.

1491
02:03:18.083 --> 02:03:19.875
I'm an independent contractor.

1492
02:03:19.958 --> 02:03:22.916
Sure. Mando. Sure you are.

1493
02:03:23.000 --> 02:03:24.375
[Grogu exclaims]

1494
02:03:33.583 --> 02:03:35.500
Can I give you a ride somewhere?

1495
02:03:35.583 --> 02:03:37.791
Actually. I was thinking I could stay here.

1496
02:03:38.583 --> 02:03:40.375
Maybe work for the New Republic.

1497
02:03:40.958 --> 02:03:43.375
Don't take this the wrong way. but...

1498
02:03:43.458 --> 02:03:45.541
I'm not sure you would fit in.

1499
02:03:45.625 --> 02:03:47.458
You know... [grunts]

1500
02:03:47.541 --> 02:03:49.791
I might have a uniform that would fit him.

1501
02:03:50.833 --> 02:03:53.708
Come on. let me buy you a drink.

1502
02:03:55.500 --> 02:03:58.041
Thank you. Mando. I owe you big time.

1503
02:03:58.125 --> 02:03:59.458
Just doing my job.

1504
02:04:00.083 --> 02:04:01.083
And keep an eye on him.

1505
02:04:02.208 --> 02:04:03.833
Your dad's one of the good ones.

1506
02:04:03.916 --> 02:04:04.916
[coos]

1507
02:04:15.958 --> 02:04:18.208
[Anzellans chattering indistinctly]

1508
02:04:18.291 --> 02:04:19.583
Come on. big guy.

1509
02:04:20.750 --> 02:04:23.125
[Anzellan 2] Watch your step. First round's on me.

1510
02:04:27.666 --> 02:04:29.166
[♪ Wistful music plays]

1511
02:04:32.291 --> 02:04:34.416
Hey. kid. Come up here.

1512
02:04:34.500 --> 02:04:35.541
[coos]

1513
02:04:41.000 --> 02:04:42.000
[grunts]

1514
02:04:54.083 --> 02:04:55.291
[The Mandalorian] Your turn.

1515
02:04:58.208 --> 02:04:59.208
Go ahead.

1516
02:05:10.791 --> 02:05:12.791
[♪ Epic music plays]

1517
02:05:27.083 --> 02:05:30.416
[♪ "The Mandalorian" theme plays]

1518
02:06:22.333 --> 02:06:24.666
[♪ Electronic music plays]

1519
02:07:34.833 --> 02:07:37.708
[♪ Ominous music plays]

1520
02:08:05.458 --> 02:08:09.208
[♪ Gentle music plays]

1521
02:09:10.625 --> 02:09:14.000
[♪ Dramatic music plays]

1522
02:09:28.666 --> 02:09:30.666
[♪ Dramatic music continues]

1523
02:10:28.250 --> 02:10:31.083
[♪ Guitar version of "The Mandalorian" theme plays]
